import React from 'react' import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import axios from 'axios'; import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { toast } from 'react-hot-toast'; export default function Profile() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [user, setUser] = useState({}); useEffect(() => { axios.get('http://localhost:3001/profile', { withCredentials: true }) .then(res => { if (res.user.Status === "Success") { setUser(res.Data); } else { toast.error(res.Data.Error) navigate('/Login'); } }) .catch(error => { toast.error("Došlo k chybě při náčítání stránky profilu. " + error); }); }, []) return ( <>

{user.jmeno} {user.prijmeni}

{user.email} - {user.role}

Účet

) }
